      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "TRENDYGOLF x G/FORE: From London to Venice, 20 Years in the making",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Since its founding in 2004, TRENDYGOLF has been driven by one mission: to bring the most fashion-forward apparel to the modern golfer. What started in London as a platform for confident, stylish players quickly grew into a global destination, curating the latest designs from the world's most exciting brands.</p><p>When TRENDYGOLF expanded into the United States, Venice Beach became its first home. Surrounded by surfboards, skateparks, and street culture, the city brought a new dimension to our vision—laid-back energy paired with bold individuality.</p><p>To mark 20 years, TRENDYGOLF has joined forces with G/FORE on a limited-edition anniversary capsule. Designed with founder Mossimo Giannulli, who hand-sketched the lightning bolt logo that runs through the collection, the capsule celebrates creativity, individuality, and the confidence to stand apart.</p><p>Tie-dye hoodies. Graphic tees. Sneakers. Hats. Each piece blends fashion and performance with the edge of Venice and the legacy of TRENDYGOLF.</p><p>From London to Venice, this is two decades of TRENDYGOLF distilled into one collaboration. Mark your calendars to shop this limited edition collection for Saturday, September 6th. </p>"
          }
        }
      },
